column2: SELECT p.objid as id, p.ra as ra, p.dec as dec, p.petroMag_u as mu, p.petroMag_g as mg, p.petroMag_r as mr, p.petroMag_i as mi, p.petroMag_z as mz, p.petroMagErr_u as eu, p.petroMagErr_g as eg, p.petroMagErr_r as er, p.petroMagErr_i as ei, p.petroMagErr_z as ez, p.extinction_u as du, p.extinction_g as dg, p.extinction_r as dr, p.extinction_i as di, p.extinction_z as dz, w.w1mpro as w1, w.w2mpro as w2, w.w3mpro as w3, w.w4mpro as w4, w.w1sigmpro as we1, w.w2sigmpro as we2, w.w3sigmpro as we3, w.w4sigmpro as we4, xm.match_dist as xmdist, s.z as redshift, s.zErr as eredshift, s.class as class, s.subclass as subclass, s.specobjid as specid FROM WISE_xmatch as xm JOIN PhotoObj AS p on xm.sdss_objid = p.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid JOIN WISE_allsky AS w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr WHERE s.class = # AND s.z > = # AND s.z < #
